graph LR
    Controller[ODH Model Controller<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-297]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    Controller -->|watches CRDs<br/>HTTPS/6443| KServe[KServe<br/>v0.11.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    Controller -->|API operations<br/>HTTPS/6443| Kubernetes[Kubernetes<br/>v1.26.4-v1.27.6<br/>REQUIRED]
    Controller -->|creates Routes<br/>via K8s API| Routes[OpenShift Routes API<br/>v3.9.0+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Conditional
    Controller -->|creates VirtualServices<br/>PeerAuthentication<br/>Telemetry| Istio[Istio / Service Mesh<br/>v1.17.4<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|creates AuthConfigs<br/>via K8s API| Authorino[Authorino<br/>v0.15.0<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|for Serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving<br/>v0.39.3<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|creates ServiceMonitors<br/>PodMonitors| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>v0.64.1<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|fetches metadata<br/>gRPC/HTTP| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>v0.1.1<br/>CONDITIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Controller -->|reads capabilities<br/>mesh config| DSC[DataScienceCluster CR<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    Controller -->|reads platform config<br/>capabilities| DSCI[DSCInitialization CR<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    Controller -->|delegates to| Maistra[Red Hat Service Mesh<br/>Maistra<br/>CONDITIONAL]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| Controller
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| Controller

    %% External Services (runtime)
    Controller -.->|enables access to| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]
    Controller -.->|enables access to| PVC[PVC Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]

    %% KServe Dependencies
    KServe -->|requires| Kubernetes
    KServe -.->|optional| Knative
    KServe -.->|optional| Istio

    %% Runtime Components (created by controller)
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Resources["OpenShift Routes<br/>NetworkPolicies<br/>VirtualServices<br/>PeerAuthentication<br/>AuthConfigs<br/>ServiceMonitors<br/>ServiceMeshMemberRoll"]

